{
  "text": "To obtain claim 2, we appeal to a standard bit of lore in non-critical string theory [CITATION_1] . Under rather general conditions, the macroscopic loop operators can be expanded as \u2113 \u2192 0 as a sum of local closed string operators,",
  "correct_citation": {
